				<td colspan="2"><span>Posted on Allakhazam:
<br />

<br />
The biggest thing to remember with this guy is that he pops from the corpse of a scareling. 
<br />

<br />
So save the scarelings till last during break in, then makesure to kill them as far from camp as possible so that he spawns away from the camp. 
<br />

<br />
He doesn't have the GIANT agro radius of everything else in the zone, so you can use agro to &quot;issolate&quot; him. 
<br />

<br />
So far the quickest way to take him down has been like doing Trak for the bard epic, Lots of super HT SKs and Fast nuking wizards. 
<br />

<br />
He is definately one to take down as fast as possible, just have a group set aside to handle the Essence of Rage imps that he spawns at intervals.
